The Seed Stalls are a set of stalls in Draynor Village owned by Olivia as part of Draynor Seed Market. Players can steal seeds from them with level 27 Thieving. When stealing from the seed stall, you get 10 Thieving experience per successful attempt. The respawn of the seeds in the stall is roughly 9 seconds.

Although all vegetable and hop seeds can be stolen from the stalls, not all of them can be bought or sold from Olivia. She will only trade with players if they have not stolen from her stalls, from Martin the Master Gardener or from a master farmer within the last 30 minutes.
